:0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T09:27:18.000Z","msg":"再介紹多一部冷門少少既抗爭電影比大家，之前無聊上網搵到哩部戲叫《搖滾吧！阿富汗》。<br />\n故事係講一班係阿富汗首都喀布爾既年青人，為左可以以圓到佢地既音樂夢係一個秘密車房組成阿富汗的第一隊Heavy Metal既Band。由於塔利班覺我音樂係象徵&quot;撒旦既舞曲&quot;，哩班熱愛音樂既年青人好想自由咁做自己鍾意既野，但同時佢地都面臨緊隨時被人帶人既威脅。當你熱愛既野被人搶走緊既時候，有幾多人會為左追求信念而去爭取？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VsRowbR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVsRowbR.jpg&h=ef2641ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a651fe828909fa6eedebb3ae4b6c6e894f5a7a5","tid":2057358,"uid":337503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24de446d9deee9c2d403d1b7664e3bce5180b2aa","tid":2057358,"uid":234589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a75f390022f7987b615367d92e8beca1f297f211","tid":2057358,"uid":337503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f887fa4b869a3315b483e51454a51555fe9afef","tid":2057358,"uid":234589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T16:39:51.000Z","msg":"紀錄片之前有外國朋友出咗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T04:12:16.000Z","msg":"有冇link"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:26:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200425/OLOHCO4QCYG3N7BWVAXY7YQEHY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200425%2FOLOHCO4QCYG3N7BWVAXY7YQEHY%2F&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XeloXq8Qv2IeoILbHjSh09rgU%3D&h=e902919e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200425%2FOLOHCO4QCYG3N7BWVAXY7YQEHY%2F&h=bbe13db6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200425/OLOHCO4QCYG3N7BWVAXY7YQEHY/</a><br />\n<br />\n條片當時被部分連登仔講成係抹黑示威者<br />\n<br />\n雖然我唔覺得係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T10:21:48.000Z","msg":"Thx <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}